summary: Initializes decoder component registries for TensorRT LLM export, mapping model identifiers to their specific decoder layer and configuration builder classes, and provides factory functions to instantiate decoder layers and their configurations based on a given model type.
business_intent: Enable a unified, extensible way to construct and configure decoder layers for multiple large language model families (e.g., Falcon, Gemma, GPT, GPTJ, Llama) when exporting models to TensorRT, simplifying integration and reducing duplication across model types.
